]]\n| Semifinal2=[[North Alabama Lions football|North Alabama]]\n| Attendance=\n}}\nThe '''2005 [[NCAA Division II Football Championship]] playoffs''' were the 32nd single-elimination tournament to determine the national champion of men's [[NCAA Division II]] college football. The championship game was held at [[Braly Municipal Stadium]] in [[Florence, Alabama]] for the 18th time.\n\n===Seeded teams===\n*[[Bloomsburg Huskies football|Bloomsburg]] \n*[[Grand Valley State Lakers football|Grand Valley State]]\n*[[Nebraska\u2013Omaha Mavericks football|Nebraska\u2013Omaha]]\n*[[North Carolina Central Eagles football|North Carolina Central]]\n*[[Presbyterian Blue Hose football|Presbyterian]]\n*[[Shepherd Rams football|Shepherd]]\n*[[Washburn Ichabods football|Washburn]]\n*[[West Texas A&M Buffaloes football|West Texas A&M]]\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n===Playoff bracket===\n{{24TeamBracket | RD1='''First Round'''<small><br />November 12<br />Campus Sites</small>\n| RD2='''Second Round'''<br /><small>November 19<br />Campus Sites</small>\n| RD3='''Quarterfinals'''<br /><small>November 26<br />Campus Sites</small>\n| RD4='''Semifinals'''<br /><small>December 3<br />Campus Sites</small>\n| RD5='''National Championship Game'''<br /><small>December 10<br />[[Braly Municipal Stadium]],<br />[[Florence, Alabama]]\n| group1=Super Region 2\n| group2=Super Region 4\n| group3=Super Region 1\n| group4=Super Region 3\n\n| RD1-seed01= 5\n| RD1-team01= '''{{cfb link|year=2005|team=Central Arkansas Bears|title=Central Arkansas}}\n| RD1-score01= '''28\n| RD1-seed02= 4\n| RD1-team02={{cfb link|year=2005|team=Albany State Golden Rams|title=Albany State}}\n| RD1-score02= 20\n| RD1-seed03= 6\n| RD1-team03= '''{{cfb link|year=2005|team=North Alabama Lions|title=North Alabama}}\n| RD1-score03= '''40\n| RD1-seed04= 3\n| RD1-team04={{cfb link|year=2005|team=Valdosta State Blazers|title=Valdosta State}}\n| RD1-score04= 13\n| RD1-seed05= 5\n| RD1-team05= '''{{cfb link|year=2005|team=Pittsburg State Gorilla